        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_5": "<p>Does it smell strong?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_6": "<p>Shipping</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_7": "<p>60-Day “Try It” Guarantee</p>",
        "ggCdVdus-lO_text": "<p>If it doesn’t live up to what we say, you’ve got 60 days to get every dollar back.<br>No hoops. No drama.</p>",
        "ggFipoBsWwP_text": "<p>No</p><p>It’s lightweight. Absorbs fast.<br>You can get dressed right after. No stains. No shine.</p>",
        "ggKZrkCgfQz_text": "<p>Men who want tighter-looking, better-feeling skin</p><p><br>without greasy lotion ruining their shirt.</p><p>If your skin’s dry…<br>If your stomach or thighs aren’t as firm as they used to be…<br>Or you just want to take care of yourself without turning it into a whole production…</p><p>This is for you.</p>",
        "ggLuQ0nuQN8_text": "<p>• Helps firm and tighten body skin<br>• Deep moisture that lasts 24 hours<br>• Improves elasticity<br>• Evens out skin tone</p>",
        "ggNgskm7d42_text": "<p>The 300ml size lasts about 2–3 months<br>if you use it daily on chest, stomach, and thighs.</p>",
        "ggR8kqovO2L_text": "<p>Right after your shower.<br>Skin still slightly damp.</p><p>Rub it in with circular motions on chest, stomach, thighs — anywhere things are starting to loosen up.</p><p><strong>Pro tip:</strong><br>Damp skin absorbs better. You’ll see results faster.</p>",
        "ggVLmbUDTCI_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:23px;\">Body Cream</span></p>",
        "ggWWrnyOmWZ_text": "<p>Ships in 24–48 hours from our Italian warehouse.<br>Free shipping on orders over €50.</p>",
        "ggYs35QKAnP_label": "Add to Cart",
        "ggYs35QKAnP_outOfStockLabel": "Out of stock",
