        "ggtOVHAQdCx_text": "<p>Deep moisture that lasts 24 hours.<br>Helps your skin hold onto water so it feels fuller and smoother.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong><br>• Long-lasting moisture<br>• Softer skin<br>• Fuller appearance</p>",
